overview: Mama's back and she's pissed! What happens when a group of idiots decide to repeat their greatest failure only making it more failure-y? Yeah. This happens. This is the sequel to the critically-hated, barely watchable Back Woods! If you thought that was bad, check this out! Luther! Deke! Mr. Havershamp! A Weird Nun! Bad Acting! Horrible Camera Work! And laser beams. LOTS of laser beams. Directed by Sir Andrew Blackhawk.
title: Back Woods 2: Mama's Beefbilly Jamboree
